{"title":"荐歌：日常（茄子蛋）","slug":"荐歌：日常（茄子蛋）","date":"2022-02-25T14:46:19.000Z","updated":"2022-02-25T14:47:24.222Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/荐歌：日常（茄子蛋）.json","excerpt":"文章来自微信公众号“科文路”，欢迎关注、互动。转发须注明出处。","covers":null,"content":"<blockquote>\n<p>文章来自微信公众号“科文路”，欢迎关注、互动。转发须注明出处。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<iframe frameborder=\"no\" border=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" width=330 height=86 src=\"//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&id=516724816&auto=1&height=66\"></iframe>\n\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<h3 id=\"推荐语\"><a href=\"#推荐语\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"推荐语\"></a>推荐语</h3><p>“我想习惯遗忘的模样，把笑容变成日常。“</p>\n<p>这首歌述说的故事一直进行的很平淡。</p>\n<p>但随着旋律继续，同样的歌词却变成了副歌的嘶吼，才让人明白这个故事的结局似乎没有那么美好。</p>\n<p>最后一段简单的吉他和弦加钢琴把整个故事拉回“日常”。</p>\n<p>故事，旋律的契合度、完整度，满分。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">日常 - 茄子蛋 (Eggplantegg)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">词：黄奇斌</span><br><span class=\"line\">曲：黄奇斌</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">我想习惯遗忘的模样</span><br><span class=\"line\">把笑容变成日常</span><br><span class=\"line\">想象着平安汇成河流</span><br><span class=\"line\">将悲伤往水里丢</span><br><span class=\"line\">我想说声 再说声</span><br><span class=\"line\">去吧</span><br><span class=\"line\">我想看着你离开</span><br><span class=\"line\">跟在你后面流浪</span><br><span class=\"line\">我猜你会回头望</span><br><span class=\"line\">不舍最后留下来</span><br><span class=\"line\">但我不曾再看到你</span><br><span class=\"line\">你总说我会在那里</span><br><span class=\"line\">我找了好长好长的日子</span><br><span class=\"line\">慢慢放下你</span><br><span class=\"line\">我想习惯遗忘的模样</span><br><span class=\"line\">把笑容变成日常</span><br><span class=\"line\">想象着平安汇成河流</span><br><span class=\"line\">将悲伤往水里丢</span><br><span class=\"line\">我想牵着你可爱的小手</span><br><span class=\"line\">朝我们的家一直走</span><br><span class=\"line\">然后说声 再说声</span><br><span class=\"line\">走吧</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><strong>都看到这儿了，不如关注每日推送的“科文路”、互动起来~</strong>i</p>\n","more":"<h3 id=\"推荐语\"><a href=\"#推荐语\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"推荐语\"></a>推荐语</h3><p>“我想习惯遗忘的模样，把笑容变成日常。“</p>\n<p>这首歌述说的故事一直进行的很平淡。</p>\n<p>但随着旋律继续，同样的歌词却变成了副歌的嘶吼，才让人明白这个故事的结局似乎没有那么美好。</p>\n<p>最后一段简单的吉他和弦加钢琴把整个故事拉回“日常”。</p>\n<p>故事，旋律的契合度、完整度，满分。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span>